Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.69,0:12:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it! Turn 3 tenpai with possible pinfu! SUPERB!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.63,0:12:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,3p!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.25,0:12:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! It came out ...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.31,0:12:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Shan't ron it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.44,0:12:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Toyotomi looks so happy, I don't want to throw him so deep into the shadowrealm right away ...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.92,0:12:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax. If it's 36p, I can easily tsumo it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.61,0:12:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaa! She drew it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What the ...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.81,0:12:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There's definitely something going on ...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.02,0:12:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,5p, huh ...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.54,0:12:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Those discards, letting me call 2s and 2p ...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.23,0:13:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,5p should pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.88,0:13:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this sudden chill?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.84,0:13:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna be like a pinzu chinitsu or something ...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.14,0:13:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.13,0:13:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What a flowmaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.25,0:13:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Phuh, tsumogiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.38,0:13:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,My shousuushii that was only 48k just became a quadruple yakuman worth 192k ...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.41,0:13:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be mean to ron him now after skipping earlier ...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.40,0:13:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What does she have with this guy?! Just ron him, ron him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.61,0:13:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll just draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.49,0:13:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Reeeee!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.04,0:14:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Tch, the 5p passed, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.72,0:14:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.96,0:14:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Gasp! Shintarou's still got a white!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.14,0:14:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Since he cut one earlier, it'll come out next turn for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.60,0:14:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon! Tsumogiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.51,0:14:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is this guy such a lucklet?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.85,0:14:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But since I can ron Shintarou's white with a {\i1}yamagoshi{\i0} trap, I'll skip ron!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.79,0:14:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon! Drop the white!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.08,0:14:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It came out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.11,0:14:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,8m ron!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.99,0:14:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.51,0:14:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.05,0:14:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ron! Ron!\N- No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.27,0:14:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ron me, okay? Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.52,0:15:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Toyotomi ....
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.80,0:15:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped, huh ...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.65,0:15:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you're so sweet! I love you, Toyotomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.99,0:15:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh, get rekt!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.70,0:15:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron! Pinfu only!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.68,0:15:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,AAAAAAAAAAAAAAA
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.73,0:15:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Mahjong is a cruel game, {\i1}baby{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.54,0:15:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Toyotomi, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.32,0:15:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wew, Toyotomi, you're such a cruel guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya made poor Akina cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.98,0:15:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What, it's just 1000 points! Is she really so arrogant that she thinks she can never deal in?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.77,0:15:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, Toyotomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.65,0:15:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Akechi, ya still got a noodle sticking from your nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.73,0:15:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have ya know that Akina ...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.76,0:16:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, Akechi. Sorry. Let's continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.06,0:16:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Tch! Girls are such a bother sometimes! C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron! Tanyao iipeikou dora dora!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Zugan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.07,0:16:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That was fast! It's only turn 6!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.27,0:16:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh, at least cheer up a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.56,0:16:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron! Pinfu sanshoku dora 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.57,0:16:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Zugan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.33,0:16:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Haitei dora dora!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.30,0:16:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Zugaaan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.41,0:16:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi menhon nan sanankou!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.34,0:16:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Zugan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.06,0:16:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Honroutou shousangen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.07,0:16:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She's totally focusing on Toyotomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's revenge! This is her revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.98,0:17:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't win a single hand cuz ya kept dealing in, ya tool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.31,0:17:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough is enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.31,0:17:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's just a drop of water in a raging fire, I'll get back some points in all last!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.38,0:17:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.63,0:17:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.21,0:17:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Chii!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.81,0:17:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.41,0:17:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Naked tanki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hehe, make sure ya don't catch a cold, bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.29,0:17:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'mma open riichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.06,0:17:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.86,0:17:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a 25p wait riichi, lads.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.95,0:17:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,TN: Dealing into an open riichi is a yakuman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.82,0:17:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.16,0:17:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There are three of each already out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.48,0:17:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Still two left. Now check Toyotomi get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.51,0:17:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, someone's got to have them in hand ...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.88,0:17:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'll draw them ...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.53,0:17:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Super Zugan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.84,0:18:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like he drew it for real!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.37,0:18:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He dropped the dora from his hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.17,0:18:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wew, this one's live!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,TN: "Live" means "not discarded yet", not "unsafe"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.24,0:18:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.43,0:18:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, tsumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.07,0:18:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.79,0:18:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be 5p ...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.96,0:18:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sketchy ...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.07,0:18:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.70,0:18:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no no no no no ...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.79,0:18:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[mindbroken by the cunny]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.87,0:18:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.87,0:18:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A- Akina ...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.25,0:19:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.54,0:19:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for ronning you for 1000 earlier ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.27,0:19:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That was my fault, I regret it now ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.40,0:19:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say stuff like that! I don't care about that any... *twitch* more at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.56,0:19:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine now, so just discard quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.67,0:19:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a face that says "I really care".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.03,0:19:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,More like "I'm really pissed".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.49,0:19:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.11,0:19:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.04,0:19:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Daisuushii tsuuiisou!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.13,0:19:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,ZUGAAAAAAAN
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.08,0:19:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Triple yakuman!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.11,0:19:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If ya cut 2p, it'd be just a single yakuman, what a retard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.96,0:19:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Zugaaaan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.11,0:19:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,With Toyotomi playing, we still somehow broke even!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.10,0:19:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It was really fun, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.93,0:20:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We should all meet up again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.19,0:20:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you so excited about, Toyotomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.46,0:20:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.64,0:20:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody said that includes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.53,0:20:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Without Toyotomi, the ones who are gonna lose are us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.21,0:20:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.63,0:20:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhh, Hayami, could you go back on that and let Toyotomi in too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.93,0:20:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Then, let's go, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.78,0:20:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhh, what about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.77,0:20:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you're the only one who lost, you can walk back home as a punishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.26,0:20:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Noooooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.18,0:20:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Akina ...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.22,0:20:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,At last given the cold shoulder by Akina: Toyotomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.10,0:21:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The cold rain pouring down on this bribery ... could it be the tears flowing from his broken heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.45,0:21:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try and stop me, mother!\NThe man Toyotomi: where will he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.57,0:21:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,TN: This line parodies a famous poster from the 1968 student unrest.
